node.accessibility_caption: @bliss is launching all the NEW! In the beauty aisle of my local @target and spotted a new line from Bliss called Disappearing Act. See no pores with the Niacinamide PC + Pore Vanish Toner! Helps purify congested pores without purging and results in smaller pores in 1 use. Or visibly shrink & reduce pores without purging with the Niacinamide PC + Pore Vanish Serum. Shrinks & bluers the appearance of pores for a smooth complexion! Head to your local @target to check out all your favs + these new additions to the collection // #ad

node.text:
G I V E A W A Y 🛒🎯

With some much new coming out lately, I want to give TWO WINNERS a $50 gift card to shop at @target ✨ Just a simple way of saying THANK YOU! It’s simple to enter:

🎯 Engage with my page by liking, saving, commenting, etc on my past several posts! Add a ☑️ in the comments when you’re done! 
🎯 Be following my page @targettherapy
BONUS: share a recent favorite post to your stores (be sure to tag my page)

PLEASE READ 👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼

Many followers have been receiving messages from PRIVATE ACCOUNTS saying you won a giveaway and need to click into a link and provide personal information including your credit card to ‘claim your prize’. These are SCAM ACCOUNTS! Please block and report them.

Winner will be announced on this post and you will receive a direct message from THIS ACCOUNT ONLY. You will NEVER be asked to click into links or for credit card information. Must be 18+ years old and live in the continental US. Giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed, or administered by or associated with Instagram or Target. GIVEAWAY ENDS 8/12/ 2021 at 11:59pm PST

node.accessibility_caption:
⭐️ GIVEAWAY ⭐️ 

I have partnered with Serenity Kids to give ONE WINNER a Ethically Sourced Meats Variety Pack and a $50 gift card to @target 🎯

Gianna and I were on a @target run and we were so excited to discover @myserenitykids is NOW AT TARGET 🛒🎯 As Moms, we all have those lazy or on-the-go days but want to make sure that our littles are still getting good quality, nutrient-dense real food and y'all, THIS IS IT 🙌🏼Serenity Kids launched their best-selling meat purees including beef, chicken, bison, salmon and turkey at select Target stores and Mama is stocking up 👏🏼 Super clean, organic, straightforward ingredients and with delicious taste, head to the baby section of your local @target store to snag Serenity Kids 🎯 We will see you there!

TO ENTER:

⭐️ Like this post
⭐️ Follow @myserenitykids
⭐️ Tag a Mama and let them know Serenity Kids is at Target (1 tag = 1 entry, unlimited)

PLEASE READ 👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼👇🏼

GIVEAWAY ENDS 8/11/2021 at 11:59pm PST // #everybitecounts #organicbabyfood #myserenitykids #serenitykids #serenitykidspartner #serenitykidsmom #target

node.text: BIG NEWS!! 🐝 I swung by my @target and was so excited to see Eczema Honey in the clean beauty section 🎯 @Eczemahoneyco is a skincare line that focuses on creating soothing products that are safe, nourishing and deliver results 🙌🏼 The CEO developed this line in hopes of finding a solution that would alleviate his children's eczema and sensitive skin and since then has been helping thousands who suffer from eczema, rashes, dermatitis, and sensitive skin concerns with this gentle skincare line 👏🏼 Formulated using high-quality and food-grade ingredients for their revitalizing & skin-loving properties, Eczema Honey is a must-have! ✨🐝 // #ad #eczemahoneyco #target #targetmusthave #sensitiveskin #clean #targetskincare #eczema
